<h3 id="safari-extensions">Safari Extensions</h3>

<p>Safari is not my go-to browser but I decided to use instead of Chrome on my Macbook due to its battery efficiency. There are not a lot of Safari extensions to choose from but the following plugins improve privacy and UX of safari;</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><table class="rouge-table"><tbody><tr><!-- <td class="rouge-gutter gl"><pre class="lineno">1
