</pre></td> --><td class="rouge-code"><pre>* Ghostery Lite
* LastPass or 1Pass
* Instapaper or Pocket
* Folx
</pre></td></tr></tbody></table></code></pre></div></div>

<p>Chrome is a lot faster than Safari and it has intensive plugins. However, the resource consumption of Chrome is higher than Safari which leads to more battery drainage.</p>

